---
---
<section class="onionomics-layers" id="tokenomics">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="layers-header">
      <h2 class="text-gradient">ONION LAYERS</h2>
      <p>Deep, disciplined, and designed to burn.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="onion-stack">
      <!-- Layer 1 -->
      <div class="onion-layer l1">
        <div class="layer-info">
          <span class="layer-num">LAYER 01</span>
          <h3>TOTAL SUPPLY</h3>
          <div class="layer-val">1,000,000,000</div>
          <p>The foundation of the swamp ecosystem. Fixed, verified, and immutable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="layer-visual">🧅</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Layer 2 -->
      <div class="onion-layer l2">
        <div class="layer-info">
          <span class="layer-num">LAYER 02</span>
          <h3>LIQUIDITY LOCK</h3>
          <div class="layer-val">100% SECURE</div>
          <p>Swamp-tested security. All LP tokens burned to the depths of the mud.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="layer-visual">🛡️</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Layer 3 -->
      <div class="onion-layer l3">
        <div class="layer-info">
          <span class="layer-num">LAYER 03</span>
          <h3>AUTO-LAYERING</h3>
          <div class="layer-val">DEFLATIONARY</div>
          <p>Every milestone peels off a layer of supply, making your $SHREK more valuable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="layer-visual">🔥</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .onionomics-layers {
    padding: 8rem 0;
    position: relative;
    background: #000;
  }

  .layers-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .layers-header h2 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
  }

  .layers-header p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .onion-stack {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .onion-layer {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 4rem;
    border-radius: 4px; /* Sharper edges */
    border-left: 10px solid var(--primary);
    background: #0A0A0A;
    transition: 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .layer-visual {
    font-size: 10rem;
    opacity: 0.05;
    position: absolute;
    right: -20px;
    bottom: -20px;
    filter: grayscale(1);
    transition: 0.5s;
  }

  .onion-layer:hover {
    transform: translateX(20px) scale(1.02);
    background: #111;
    border-left-width: 20px;
    box-shadow: -20px 0 50px rgba(164, 198, 57, 0.1);
  }

  .onion-layer:hover .layer-visual {
    opacity: 0.2;
    transform: scale(1.1) rotate(-10deg);
  }

  .layer-info {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .layer-num {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 950;
    color: var(--primary);
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
  }

  .layer-info h3 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .layer-val {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .layer-info p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 500px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  /* Variations for each layer */
  .l2 { border-left-color: #7AC143; }
  .l3 { border-left-color: #A4C639; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .onion-layer { padding: 2rem; flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
    .layer-val { font-size: 2rem; }
    .layer-visual { font-size: 5rem; top: 10px; right: 10px; bottom: auto; }
  }
</style>
